amma%E1%B9%AD%E1%B9%ADh%C4%81na" title="Kammaṭṭhāna">Kammaṭṭhāna</a></span><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Anussati" title="Anussati">Recollection</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Anapanasati" title="Anapanasati">Mindfulness of Breathing</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Samatha" title="Samatha">Serenity meditation</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Vipassan%C4%81" title="Vipassanā">Insight meditation</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Shikantaza" title="Shikantaza">Shikantaza</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Zazen" title="Zazen">Zazen</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/K%C5%8Dan" title="Kōan">Kōan</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Mandala" title="Mandala">Mandala</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Tonglen" title="Tonglen">Tonglen</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Tantra" title="Tantra">Tantra</a>)</div>
